title: IBD Nail Wipes- Lint Free 80ct
description:
An economical and sanitary way to remove tacky Gel residue with Cleanser Plus and to dust nails prior to product application.
Fiberless pads will not scratch or dull surfaces like other wipes can. You can actually see the difference!
Helps you achieve that beautiful shine every time.
Can be used with any polish remover as an alternative to cotton.
Use one per client.
